{"product_id":"cleaning-tablets","title":"Ultrasonic Boosting Tablets","description":"\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePatented shape, size and formula to optimise ultrasonic cleaning \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003eUnique formula engineered to safely and effectively help remove stubborn bacteria\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003eFresh mint scent to neutralise odours and freshen the taste of your oral appliance\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003eUnlike traditional tablets, no harmful chemicals such as SLS, sodium benzoate and persulfates\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWhile the Dental Pod acts as the superpowered toothbrush, the cleaning tablets act as the toothpaste. Using patented technology to amplify ultrasonic cleaning and help remove stubborn stains and bacteria, these tablets are the perfect partner for your Dental Pod.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"row\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"fourteen columns offset-by-one\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Dental Pod","offers":[{"title":"1 Box","offer_id":44090853753109,"sku":"TB-P30-EU","price":12.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"3 Boxes","offer_id":44090853785877,"sku":"BDL-TB-3-EU","price":38.97,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"6 Boxes","offer_id":44090853818645,"sku":"BDL-TB-6-EU","price":70.14,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0699\/9569\/2309\/files\/1_4482266f-efef-423b-8fed-5c4726a0cf14.png?v=1765819976","url":"https:\/\/zimadental.nl\/products\/cleaning-tablets","provider":"ZIMA DENTAL EU","version":"1.0","type":"link"}